org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.systems.arm

Class ArmSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.systems.System
      • org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.systems.arm.ArmSystem

  • public class ArmSystem
extends System
    Arm System rotates the arm up and down through angular motion. The arm moves using a potentiometer and ramps as it approaches the top of the robot and bottom of the robot to prevent damage to the arm
